/*
  # Global Pipeline Network Expansion

  ## Purpose
  Adds comprehensive global oil, gas, and LNG pipeline infrastructure covering all major
  regions: Middle East, Russia/FSU, Europe, North America, Africa, Asia-Pacific, South America,
  and Central Asia. Each entry represents a major trunk pipeline with its route midpoint
  coordinates, capacity, status, and known incident history.

  ## Changes
  - New rows in `critical_infrastructure` table (infra_type = 'pipeline')
  - Covers ~130+ additional major pipelines worldwide
  - All statuses set appropriately (intact/damaged/destroyed)

  ## Notes
  1. Coordinates represent approximate route midpoints or key facilities
  2. Existing Middle East pipeline entries are NOT duplicated
  3. No DDL changes — data-only migration
*/

