('Strait of Malacca Oil Transit (Tanker Route)', 'Malaysia', 'Southeast Asia', 'highway', 'intact', 2.5000, 102.0000, 'Narrow sea lane between Malaysian Peninsula and Sumatra. 15.7 million bpd tanker transit daily. World''s busiest shipping chokepoint after Strait of Hormuz.', '', 'Any blockage would force 3,200km detour around Lombok/Sunda Strait. China imports 80% of oil through here.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strait_of_Malacca'),
